org.forgerock.openidm.tools.scriptedbundler

Class CustomObjectType

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.forgerock.openidm.tools.scriptedbundler.CustomBaseObject
      • org.forgerock.openidm.tools.scriptedbundler.CustomObjectType

  • public class CustomObjectType
extends CustomBaseObject
    A single connector configuration objectType, contained in CustomConfiguration. Given a JSON configuration such as: 
    
      "objectTypes" : [
          {
              "name" : "group",
              "id" : "__GROUP__",
              "type" : "object",
              "nativeType" : "__GROUP__",
              "objectClass" : "ObjectClass.GROUP_NAME",
              "flags" : [
                  "NOT_READABLE",
                  "NOT_RETURNED_BY_DEFAULT"
              ],
              "properties" : [
                  {
                      "name" : "name",
                      "type" : "string",
                      "required" : true,
                      "nativeName" : "__NAME__",
                      "nativeType" : "string"
                      "items" : [
                          {
                              "type" : "object",
                              "properties" : [{
                                  "name" : "uid",
                                  "type" : "string"
                              }]
                          }
                      ]
                  },{
                      ...
                  }
              ]
          }
      ]
    this object represents a single objectType array element.
